Gem
===

File uploading for Zend Framework 

Introduction
============ 

BinderClip allows for easy file uploading and control over uploaded files. 
BinderClip works as an plugin to Zend_Db_Table

Installation
============

* Latest copy of Zend_Db_Table from the incubator.

Credits
=======

BinderClip is inspired by PaperClip and UploadColumn that are available for 
ruby on rails.

